M|Exte|it|Intercom, *RICE Prioritization* (2016) — Origin of RICE framework
M|Exte|it|Sean McBride, *ICE Scoring* (2012) — Lightweight prioritization
M|Exte|it|Luke Hohmann, *Innovation Games* (2006) — Buy-a-Feature and other collaborative methods
M|Exte|it|Noriaki Kano, *Kano md* (1984) — cs satisfaction framework
